"content": "哈......哈......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩？怎麼跑得那麼急？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#4$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那些羅德島的人呢？", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#4$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就直說了吧，聽好，亞歷山德莉娜·維娜·維多利亞。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭和博士被“灰禮帽”要求繼續完成那場交易，他們必須去尋找飛空艇的位置。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威靈頓公爵的軍隊已經進入了這個地塊，開斯特公爵的增援恐怕也到了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都對薩卡茲那架飛空艇的技術勢在必得，他們都無法接受自己的競爭對手首先獲得技術上的優勢。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾伯特區已經成了公爵們角力的圍場。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，果然是那些人的一貫作風。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那條廣播呢？你說的，能推動大公爵們正式進攻這裡的廣播——", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#10$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲小姐說，她會盡量做到。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡量做到？這是什麼意思？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#5$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說，等到日出。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白了。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假設大公爵們依然會採取正面行動，我們還有多少時間？", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果伊內絲小姐成功......溫德米爾公爵的高速軍艦會在日出後不久靠近這裡。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們在這裡聚集了很多人。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些不在這裡的人，應該也已經收到消息了，願意跟著我們的人會跟上隊伍的。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我建議在大公爵的軍艦正式靠近之前，我們應該繼續在這裡等待。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼下的情況......走在街道上不是個好主意。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是威靈頓還是開斯特，他們對有可能妨礙他們的人都從不手軟。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我們最好現在就出發。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封鎖牆邊的幾個薩卡茲駐軍營地被襲擊了，很可能就是某位大公爵的部隊幹的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們應該趁著現在還是夜裡，盡量靠近那些封鎖牆防守比較薄弱的地帶。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更重要的是......我們要讓還躲在窗戶後面張望的那些人知道，我們說的是真的。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次撤離不是個為了騙取他們僅剩儲備的陰謀，不是個薩卡茲剿滅他們的陷阱。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重新建立信任是困難的，而唯一的方法不過是——", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他們看見實際的行動。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G1_interrogat_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喏，這幾本是你上次托我帶的書。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可在那些倫蒂尼姆的圖書館裡找了半天，我又不懂維多利亞語，最後是抓了個可憐的菲林才幫你找到。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你有時還會在另一個空白的本子上寫寫畫畫。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不光看書，還會自己寫東西？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒去過卡茲戴爾，但聽說那裡的地窖裡甚至還有間薩卡茲的大學。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是那裡的老師？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我和你一樣，為人賣命。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些書真的這麼好看？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是些差不多的結論，只是相似的情形一遍遍上演。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作者們就只能繼續得出這些差不多的結論。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同樣覺得膩煩。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德將軍讓我們把你關在這裡，卻一直沒有進一步的指令......", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是怎麼得罪他了？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，他只是覺得，對於我來說，監獄更安靜。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡......更方便我做些真正願意去做的事。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真正願意去做的事情就是看書？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你可真夠無聊的。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說......我們薩卡茲很快就要有個真正的好消息了。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能夠震撼整片大地的好消息！", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無非是又一場戰爭。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有沒有人和你說過，跟你聊天很沒勁？", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_393_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是真有。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......更沒勁了。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，我要換班了。你老實在這裡待著吧。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了答應我的，幫你找書的報酬——", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "王庭軍士兵的身影晃晃悠悠地消失在監獄走廊的盡頭，很快，另一串腳步聲就會響起。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷等待著。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是只有寂靜。"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g9_airshipdockcorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船員們都已經登上飛空艇了。", "name": "王庭軍士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明椒。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......我在！", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看過一本......叫《薩卡茲戰爭史》的書嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒有。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該看看，我的抽屜裡有一本，你可以拿去。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是個很精彩的故事嗎？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一本戰爭史。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您已經說了......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你就不該問這樣的問題。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不認同這本書中的幾乎一切觀點，軟弱，悲哀，破碎。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我仍然承認，那是本浸透著鮮血的書。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位作者又會怎麼描述我們眼下的這場戰爭呢？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#9$1", "focu